Detailed Description

Objects of this class will expand routes from lists of IDs to strings and/or coordinates.

This is done by sending packets to the map module.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum RouteExpander::state [private]
 

The states of this class.

Enumeration values:
IDTRANS  Sending and receiving IDTranslation.
TOP_REGION  Sending and receiving top region request.
EXPAND  Sending and receiving expand route request.
DONE  Expand concatenated ok.
ERROR  Something went wrong when processing any part of the task for this class.

)  [private]
 

Loop the landmarks in one route-part and select which ones to keep in the route.

The selection is performed based on the importance of the landmarks and the length of the route-part.
